{"tid":1820731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有位台灣女手足，叫我幫佢多謝咁多位香港手足。","createTime":"2020-01-11T16:40:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T02:48:04.000Z","uid":25250,"like":118,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"f2228eb5f1cb15a230d288baf71b5138037abbe0","tid":1820731,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T16:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUaGcfM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUaGcfM.jpg&h=3920a1ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VzgRzub.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVzgRzub.png&h=c2c8f320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只係短短幾句，希望各位見到呢個世界上有人支持我地，雖然連登已經5毛攻佔左，但係我想同咁多位今年一齊繼續行下去，直到勝利為止"},{"pid":"6c30d9efe35ce673a458bb2e507a7d7afefe502a","tid":1820731,"uid":25250,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T16:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sYp0sP3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsYp0sP3.png&h=587cf65a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連貼錯圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a352794fda7fc8668286eabd74e1782ce52782e","tid":1820731,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T16:41:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"dad0ed01627c67bc8bea46cb3ce7f41ded6992e9","tid":1820731,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T16:44:26.000Z","msg":"咁多位有無野想同台灣手足講返？"},{"pid":"d7f694a02c067cedbe43c4b09c591020fca8cc44","tid":1820731,"uid":27725,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T16:46:25.000Z","msg":"佢太客氣了"},{"pid":"32be1f34aa988627f9789a2e4e5ead86f8e5192d","tid":1820731,"uid":27725,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01